  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients operated with a vertical rectus abdominis musculocutaneus flap after
             abdominoperineal resection for advanced pelvic cancer.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pre or perioperative knowledge of disseminated malignancy

          -  Unable to follow the control program

          -  Known allergy to pig

          -  Compromised immune defense

          -  Artificial heart valve or recent (&lt; 3 months) implanted foreign body

          -  Age &lt; 18 years
      </textblock>
